<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed my-4 text-base" style="font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif">The company’s approach emphasizes accuracy, cost-effectiveness, and maximizing energy generation while optimizing project costs, critical factors for EPC companies’ profitability and client satisfaction. With experience across residential, commercial, and industrial rooftop installations in diverse Indian states, Heaven Designs understands the practical challenges that EPC companies face and delivers designs that are not just technically compliant but also practical to install and maintain.</p>
